isis.stitle: DT/DTI-466 A and B Series DT/DTI/DTA-466 C Diesel Engine Diagnostics (1993) - ENGINE DIAGNOSTIC TEST PROCEDURES - DT/DTI/DTA - 466 C SERIES DIESEL ENGINES - SUFFICIENT CLEAN FUEL DT/DTI/DTA-466 C Engines (With Robert Bosch "MW" or "A" Fuel Injection Pump) - Sufficient Clean Fuel

svcproc.title: Sufficient Clean Fuel
svcproc.para: If fuel is satisfactory, enter OK in 1st check box. Drain water or remove foreign substances as required. Record any corrective action taken in the comments section of the form.
